<tr id="L370"><td><a href="#L370">370</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: Archer comes in and sits down.</td></tr>

<tr id="L371"><td><a href="#L371">371</a></td><td>T'POL:  Lieutenant Reed told me you went to the surface.</td></tr>

<tr id="L372"><td><a href="#L372">372</a></td><td>ARCHER:  I spoke to Doctor Oratt. I didn't tell you because I didn't want you to try and talk me out of it.</td></tr>

